CAS Stress application
======================

A stress tool for Cassandra 2.0 CAS implementation, based on java-driver
stress example (https://github.com/datastax/java-driver/tree/2.0/driver-examples/stress)
and jepsen's cassandra-transacion app (https://github.com/aphyr/jepsen/blob/master/src/jepsen/cassandra.clj#L228-L290).

Usage
-----

1. Install the java-driver, 2.0 branch, locally:
    
    git clone https://github.com/datastax/java-driver.git
    git checkout 2.0
    mvn install

2. Build CAS Torturer
    
    ./bin/build

3. Run the torturer
    
    ./bin/torture

See ./bin/torture -h for more details on the options available.
